title: NFL Week 9 Preview & Trade Deadline Recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 9 Preview & Trade Deadline Recap
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith look back at some big trades that happened in the NFL before the trading deadline and then use predictive analytics to preview all of the Week 9 matchups. Former New York Giants offensive lineman Shaun O'Hara joins the show to talk with Cynthia about the impact of Duane Brown on the Seattle Seahawks.
